snippet.title: Nirvana - Smells Like Teen Spirit - Drum Cover in VR
snippet.description:
Join our Discord community to never miss updates! https://discord.gg/paradiddle

VR drum cover played in Paradiddle: we're on Steam for PC VR (https://store.steampowered.com/app/685240/) or App Lab for Quest (https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3592251770823318/). This Nirvana cover is specifically from our Version 1.0 update that's going to come out later this year.
